sentences: Q5 is an American hard rock/heavy metal band from Seattle, Washington, United States, who formed in 1983.
Their first studio album, titled Steel the Light, came out in 1984.
However, the group faced internal divisions that ultimately ended the project before the 1980s came to a close.

In 2014, Q5 re-formed to perform at the Sweden Rock Festival, and the band members involved found that the one-off event was not enough, deciding to continue on with the revamped version of the group.
Their first studio album, 1984's Steel the Light, earned praise from several critics.
Q5 signed on with Polygram for their 1985 sophomore release, When The Mirror Cracks, but the writing was already on the wall.
